{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "小弟与谢晓峰在客栈用餐，小弟每样只尝一口便放下筷子，结账时发现谢晓峰身无分文。小弟故意走向武当曹寒玉、金陵袁家兄弟的酒桌，揭露谢晓峰身份，挑起杀叔杀兄之仇后趁乱溜走。小弟独行长街，内心充满孤苦悲愤，拦下红旗镖局马车，以指法轻松击败镖师铁掌胡非，与车中猫一样的女人互相调情。谢晓峰突然现身车厢，小弟发现这女人竟是谢晓峰的旧日情人，心碎之下怒骂\"婊子\"，狂笑着撞门跳车而去。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "旁人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小子也不知是暴发户，还是饿疑了！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些菜都是我喜欢吃的，只可惜平时很难吃得到！",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "只要你高兴，能吃多少，就吃多少。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你吃得不多？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "若是吃一口就已尝出来滋味，又何必吃得太多？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "text": "看账来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胖掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "这是八两银子一桌的菜，外加酒水，一共是十两四钱。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "text": "不贵。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "胖掌柜",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "小号做生意一向规矩。连半分钱都不会多算客官的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "加上小账赏钱。我们就给他十二两怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你要照顾我，我吃饭当然该你付钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么还不付！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "因为我连一两银子都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "speaker_name": "曹寒玉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你也懂剑？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "text": "据说昔年有位徐鲁子徐大师，铸剑之术，天下无双，据说他曾应武当第七代掌门之邀，以西方精铁之英，用武当解剑池的水，铸成了七柄利剑，由掌门人传给门下剑术最高的七大弟子，人在剑在，死后才交回掌门收执。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "text": "却不知这柄剑是否其中之一？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "好眼力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "贵姓？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我姓袁，他姓曹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "text": "莫非就是武当七大弟子中，最年轻英俊的曹寒玉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "好眼力。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "那么阁下想必就是金陵紫衣老家的大公子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我是老二，我叫袁次云，他才是我的大哥袁飞云，就坐在他身旁，唇上已有了微髋。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_bu_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "这位呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_bu_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "彩凤不与寒鸦同飞，这位想必也是名门世家的少爷公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "布衣少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_bu_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "很好。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里总算有个人是跟他无冤无仇的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "就是那个本来该付账，身上却连一两银子都没有的人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我们都跟他有冤仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "好像有一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "有什么冤？什么仇？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "贤昆仱是不是有位叔父，江湖人称千红剑客？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "这位曹公子是不是有位兄长，单名一个‘冰’字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "他们两位是不是死在神剑山庄的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "speaker_name": "袁次云",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "难道你说的那个人就是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_yuan_ci_yun",
      "text": "他就是翠云峰，绿水湖，神剑山庄的三少爷谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "speaker_name": "曹寒玉",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你就是谢晓峰？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_cao_han_yu",
      "text": "我就是。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你知不知道吃白食的，最好的法子是什么？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_pang_zhang_gui",
      "text": "就是先找几个人混战一场，自己再悄悄溜走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你想死？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "好漂亮的头发，好香。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你想干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我想死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "那容易得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我就知道我找对了地方，也找对了人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "他既然这么想死，你为什么不索性成全了他？胡大爷几时变得连人都不敢杀了？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "你几时见过我胡非杀过这样的无名小辈？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "你怎么知道他是个无名的小辈？他年纪虽轻，可是年轻人里名气大过你的也有不少，说不定他就是武当派的曹寒玉，也说不定他就是江南紫衣袁家的大少爷，你心里一定就在顾忌着他们，所以才不敢出手。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "这位胡大爷莫非就是红旗镖局的铁掌胡非？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "想不到你居然还有点见识。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我也想不到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "想不到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "想不到红旗镖局居然有这么大的威风，这么大的气派，连镖局一个小小的镖师，都能摆得出这么大的排场来。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我的排场大小，跟你有什么关系？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "一点关系都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你姓什么？叫什么？是什么来历？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我既没有姓名，也没有来历，我……我……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我虽不杀无名小辈，今日却不妨破例一次。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "你虽然肯破例了，我却又改变了主意，又不想死了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "胡大镖头为什么忽然变得如此多礼？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "你……你这个吃里扒外的贼人……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我吃里扒外？我吃了你什么？凭你一个小小的镖师，就能养得起我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "一直都是我在养他，不是他在养我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "最近你吃得太多，应该少坐车，多走路。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "可是我一个人坐在车里又害怕，你说该怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "你想不想找个人陪你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我当然想，想得要命，可是，我在这里人地生疏，又能找得到谁呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我只甩那种本来就像鼻涕的男人，你像不像鼻鼻涕？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "不像。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你好大的胆子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "我的胆子一向不小。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你知道我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "你是个女人，很漂亮的女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "漂亮的女人，都有男人的，你知道我是谁的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "不管你以前是谁的，现在总是我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "可是……可是我连你的名字都不知道。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "我没有名字，我……我是个没爹没娘的小杂种。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你心里在想什么？是不是想强奸我！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 331,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你又来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "我又来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道你从小就是个风流公子，你的女人多得连数都数不清。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么你为什么不让我也有个女人，难道你要我做一辈子和尚？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你不必做和尚，可是这个女人不行。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "因为我是他的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "几年不见，你又瘦了，是不是因为女人太多？还是因为想我想瘦的？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么不告诉我，这位小弟弟是什么人，跟你有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你笑什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "我笑你，我早就知道你是什么人了，又何必别人来告诉我？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "speaker_name": "猫一样的女人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你真的知道我是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_mao_yi_yang_de_nv_ren",
      "text": "你是个婊子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    }
